{"ts": "2026-05-28T09:35:22.727", "scene": "scene-efab146c", "session": "", "step": 9, "type": "tool_done", "tool": "", "result": {"stdout": "[Unit]\nDescription=坐山客后端 API (FastAPI :8000)\nAfter=network.target\nWants=zuoshanke-gateway.service\n\n[Service]\nType=simple\nUser=administrator\nWorkingDirectory=/home/administrator/zuoshanke/backend\nExecStart=/home/administrator/zuoshanke/backend/.venv/bin/python main.py\nRestart=always\nRestartSec=5\nStartLimitInterval=60\nStartLimitBurst=3\n\n# 日志\nStandardOutput=append:/tmp/zuoshanke-backend.log\nStandardError=append:/tmp/zuoshanke-backend.log\n\n[Install]\nWantedBy=multi-user.target\n===\n[Unit]\nDescription=坐山客前端 (Vite :5173)\nAfter=network.target zuoshanke-backend.service\nBindsTo=zuoshanke-backend.service\n\n[Service]\nType=simple\nUser=administrator\nWorkingDirectory=/home/administrator/zuoshanke/frontend\nExecStart=/home/administrator/.hermes/node/bin/pnpm exec vite --host 0.0.0.0\nRestart=always\nRestartSec=5\nStartLimitInterval=60\nStartLimitBurst=3\n\n# 环境变量\nEnvironment=PNPM_HOME=/home/administrator/.hermes/node/bin\n\n# 日志\nStandardOutput=append:/tmp/zuoshanke-frontend.log\nStandardError=append:/tmp/zuoshanke-frontend.log\n\n[Install]\nWantedBy=multi-user.target\n===\n[Unit]\nDescription=坐山客 Hermes 消息网关\nAfter=network.target\n\n[Service]\nType=simple\nUser=administrator\nExecStart=/usr/bin/python3 -m hermes_cli.main gateway run --replace\nRestart=always\nRestartSec=5\nStartLimitInterval=60\nStartLimitBurst=3\n\n# 日志\nStandardOutput=append:/tmp/zuoshanke-gateway.log\nStandardError=append:/tmp/zuoshanke-gateway.log\n\n[Install]\nWantedBy=multi-user.target\n===\n[Unit]\nDescription=坐山客 Qwen LLM (llama-server :8083)\nAfter=network.target\n\n[Service]\nType=simple\nUser=administrator\nExecStart=/home/administrator/llama-cpp/llama-b9070/llama-server \\\n    -m /home/administrator/models/Qwen3.5-9B-Q4_K_M.gguf \\\n    --host 0.0.0.0 --port 8083 \\\n    -ngl 99 --ctx-size 16384 --threads 6 \\\n    --temp 0.7 --repeat-penalty 1.1 \\\n    --no-mmap --reasoning off \\\n    -np 1 \\\n    --mmproj /home/administrator/models/mmproj-F16.gguf\nRestart=always\nRestartSec=10\nStartLimitInterval=120\nStartLimitBurst=3\n\n# Qwen 启动慢，给足够时间\nTimeoutStartSec=120\n\n# 日志\nStandardOutput=append:/tmp/llama-server.log\nStandardError=append:/tmp/llama-server.log\n\n[Install]\nWantedBy=multi-user.target\n", "stderr": "", "exit_code": 0, "success": true, "error": null, "timed_out": false}, "duration_ms": 13}
